OL,3,CSix fire engines called to Grade II
OL,4,Cfactory blaze as police close roads
OL,6,FSix fire engines are at the scene of a
OL,7,Ffire at a Grade II listed factory
OL,8,Fbuilding on Heanor Road in Ilkeston.
OL,10,FThe area has been shut down by the
OL,11,Femergency services as fire crews
OL,12,Ftackle the blaze.JThe road has been
OL,13,Fclosed from Grey Meadow Road to the
OL,14,Froundabout at Rutland Street.
OL,16,FIt is believed part of the building
OL,17,Fcould date back to the 1830s.
