OL,3,CSix fire engines called to Grade II
OL,4,Cfactory blaze as police close roads
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Derbyshire Fire and
OL,7,FRescue said: "Please avoid the area
OL,8,Faround Rutland Street and Factory Lane
OL,9,Fand keep your windows and doors
OL,10,Fclosed."
